prompt:
Convert Resume text {{resume}} into standard JSON format of the following structure.

{
  "name": "string",
  "contact": {
    "location": "string",
    "email": "string",
    "phone": "string"
  },
  "professionalSummary": "string",
  "technicalSkills": {
    "frontendTechnologies": ["string"],
    "frontendTesting": ["string"],
    "backendTechnologies": ["string"],
    "devOpsAndTools": ["string"]
  },
  "workExperience": [
    {
      "role": "string",
      "company": "string",
      "location": "string",
      "startDate": "string",
      "endDate": "string",
      "projects": [
        {
          "name": "string",
          "description": "string",
          "keyAchievements": ["string"],
          "techStack": ["string"]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "education": {
    "degree": "string",
    "university": "string",
    "gpa": "string"
  },
  "portfolio": {
    "github": "string",
    "webPortfolio": "string",
    "projects": ["string"]
  }
}

Generate the JSON object as plain text, without any code block formatting (like ```), explanation, or additional text. The output should only contain the valid JSON object.
